rows.label: tlk45370154_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Superbia is a military nation. As such,
all of the people organizing national
affairs are military officers.

rows.label: tlk45370154_01_msg0002
rows.name:
The Departments of Finance,
Meteorology, Justice, Security...
all are run as military branches.

rows.label: tlk45370154_01_msg0003
rows.name:
To avoid power being monopolized by
a select few, nobody is stationed
in the same place for too long.

rows.label: tlk45370154_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Morph was over the moon when he was
assigned to administrate the largely
peaceful territory of Gula...

rows.label: tlk45370154_01_msg0005
rows.name:
But in the end, he failed to even
serve his full term in office.
